  <summary date="2021-04-20T17:51:59Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Department of Veterans Affairs Employee Fairness Act of 2021

This bill repeals provisions excluding any matter or question concerning professional conduct or competence; peer review; or the establishment, determination, or adjustment of employee compensation from the applicability of collective bargaining rights for Veterans Health Administration employees.</summary>
